com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable

Class DataRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable.DataRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PublicCloneable, StringEncodable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class DataRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, PublicCloneable, StringEncodable
    DataRecord is a single record of DataTable. When created separately from a table, DataRecord may have its own TableFormat describing record fields and other options.
